Jason,

Tow that bus to Boulder and use our garage this weekend. Probably not an
option for you. Seriously, get yourself some plastic drape it over the back
of the bus and tent it off on the ground behind you and throw a small heater
in there. If you don't have a heater then drag some 5 gallon buckets of hot
water out, it is highly inefficient but it will help.

